     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"Based in our contact centre, our accessibility champions have an in-depth understanding of accessible travel in London. Our champions have received enhanced training and will be able to provide you with a better service, as well as share their knowledge with colleagues.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "To speak to a customer services adviser about accessibility on any TfL service call 0343 222 1234*.",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail:\u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"mailto:TfLAccessibility@tfl.gov.uk\"\u003eTfLAccessibility@tfl.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "You can write to us at:",
     "TfL Customer Services\u003cbr /\u003e4th Floor\u003cbr /\u003e14 Pier Walk\u003cbr /\u003eLondon SE10 0ES",
     "For service updates and news follow \u003ca href=\"https://twitter.com/TfLAccess\"\u003e@TfLAccess on Twitter\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "To find out more about \u003ca href=\"/transport-accessibility/learn-to-use-public-transport\"\u003etravel mentoring\u003c/a\u003e contact us on 020 3054 4361*.",
     "If you would like to make a booking for assisted travel on London Overground or TfL Rail, please call 24 hours in advance on 0343 222 2000* between 08:00 and 20:00, Monday to Sunday (excluding Christmas Day). You can also book online on the \u003ca href=\"https://passenger-assist.org/assisttravel/TravelAssist.aspx?LAYOUT=BLANK\u0026TOCCode=DLkP6_p3jo9SUbFl9cJ_ZQ\"\u003epassenger assist\u003c/a\u003e website.",
     "For more informationÂ about London Overground assistance, please visit \u003ca href=\"http://www.arrivaraillondon.co.uk/customer-information/accessibility\"\u003eLondon Overground Rail Operations\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "* \u003ca href=\"/corporate/terms-and-conditions/tfl-call-charges\"\u003eFind out about TfL call charges\u003c/a\u003e ."
    ],
